      • get

        public Object get(String s)
           throws NumberFormatException,
                  ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException,
                  NoSuchElementException
        We are able to fetch properties or expressions (i.e previous expression) using this single call, despite the fact that each of these types of results lie in different data structures m_expressions and m_props. This allows us to easily perform expression evaluation without need or concern over which 'type' of $ reference we are dealing with
        Throws:
        NumberFormatException
        ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException
        NoSuchElementException
